    <abstract id="aspace_ec44ba3c95eca8e15e8512a630e1de59">The International Union of United Brewery, Flour, Cereal, Soft Drink and Distillery Workers of America, Local 267 in Logansport, Pennsylvania, began as United Distillery Workers of North America, Local 942 at Logansport Distilling Company, Inc.  This collection includes information from 1936 to 1959 regarding both Local 942 and Local 267.</abstract>
